---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="FAQ | Vibe Test Labs"
  description="Frequently asked questions about Vibe Test Labs - shipping, returns, orders, tracking, and more."
>
  <section style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem 1.5rem;line-height:1.8;">
    <h1 style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p style="color:#888;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Got a question? We've got answers. If you don't see what you're looking for, reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@vibetestlabs.com">support@vibetestlabs.com</a>.</p>

    <div style="border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
        <summary style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;list-style:none;">Where do you ship to?</summary>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">We currently ship within the <strong>United States only</strong>. We hope to expand to international shipping in the future - stay tuned!</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
        <summary style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;list-style:none;">How long does shipping take?</summary>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">Orders are typically processed within <strong>1 business day</strong> and delivered within <strong>2 business days</strong> via standard shipping. You'll receive a tracking number by email once your order ships.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
        <summary style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;list-style:none;">How do I track my order?</summary>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">Once your order ships, you'll get a confirmation email with your tracking number. You can also visit our <a href="/track-order">Track Your Order</a> page and enter your tracking number to see real-time updates.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
        <summary style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;list-style:none;">What is your return policy?</summary>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">We want you to be completely happy with your purchase. If you experience <em>any</em> issue with your order - damaged items, wrong product, non-delivery, or anything else - we'll issue a <strong>full refund, no questions asked</strong>. Just contact us within 30 days of your order date.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
        <summary style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;list-style:none;">How do I request a refund?</summary>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">Just email us at <a href="mailto:support@vibetestlabs.com">support@vibetestlabs.com</a> with your order number and a brief description of the issue. We'll take care of it right away - usually within 1-2 business days.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
        <summary style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;list-style:none;">What payment methods do you accept?</summary>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">We accept all major credit and debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover), as well as PayPal, Apple Pay, and Google Pay. All payments are processed securely through Shopify.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
        <summary style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;list-style:none;">Are the products on Vibe Test Labs tested by real people?</summary>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">Yes! Every product featured on our site has been reviewed and tested by our team. We score products on quality, value, design, and real-world performance. We only feature products we'd actually recommend.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
        <summary style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;list-style:none;">Can I cancel or change my order?</summary>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">Orders are processed quickly, so cancellations or changes may not always be possible after placement. Please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@vibetestlabs.com">support@vibetestlabs.com</a> as soon as possible and we'll do our best to help.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
        <summary style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;list-style:none;">I have a question that's not listed here. How do I get in touch?</summary>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">We're happy to help! Send us an email at <a href="mailto:support@vibetestlabs.com">support@vibetestlabs.com</a> and we'll get back to you within 1 business day.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
